<br>
I am getting ready to hit level 28.  Neaoh is 29 and Askyn is 30 and we want to do some leveling there.  I know I probably need to hit level 30, so that is most likely what I will do.<br>
<br>
What I am asking from you is directions to the zone. In detail now, hehe, and don't use that south, west, north stuff.  use left, right and straight type directions.  I don't believe in sense heading as you can tell.<br>
<br>
Also, where to hunt and what to hunt at level 30 once in the zone. Is there a bank we can get to?  Can any of us sell there?  Is it too camped to worry about?<br>
<br>
Thanks for the info in advance.<br>
<br>
Azariel<br>
Uriel <br>
