<br>
Seriously though, you need levitate and camo / invis to get around in there.  It is a loooong drop past lots of orcs to get to the bottom.  There is a dwarven outpost at the bottom w/ a bank and merchants.  If you get trained down there, the Dwarven guards WILL NOT HELP!!  I think they enjoy seeing you get your ass handed to you.<br>
<br>
