<br>
The blue mobs there are undercons. A snow dervish will tear through a 30th level caster in a matter of seconds and they have more HP than usual.<br>
<br>
Don't get me wrong, you guys should get to Velious soon-ish, but wait till Gaff or myself have a chance to port ya there and have that evac button ready. Then we can show you the rygor camp, and the way to the crystal caverns.<br>
<br>
